| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3184 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: af61c0a6-c4da-5ae4-8a3c-4e7611c2aaa6"
